descriptionHtml:
This is the official mobile app of the Atlanta Hawks & State Farm Arena. It delivers an unrivaled and unique interactive experience for both Hawks fans and event-goers alike!

FEATURES INCLUDE:

Hawks:

• Seamlessly manage and/or purchase your tickets, upgrades, parking, experiences, and more.

• Interactive box scores with players stats, sortable play-by-play, and shot-tracking.

title: Hawks + State Farm Arena

creator: Atlanta Hawks
descriptionHtml:
This is the official mobile app of the Atlanta Hawks & State Farm Arena. It delivers an unrivaled and unique interactive experience for both Hawks fans and event-goers alike!


FEATURES INCLUDE:

- Seamlessly manage and/or purchase your tickets, upgrades, parking, experiences, and more

- New menu functionality from the nav bar allows you to be 2 taps or less away from any desired destination at all times.

- Hawks version of live gamecast.  Get real time shot charts, statistics, and a game flow to see what team has been in control at any given time.

- Browse roster breakdowns, player bios, stats, and photos.

- View recent, current, and upcoming games on the interactive team calendar.

- Browse the latest stories, articles, photo galleries, and videos.

- Membership Portal allows fans to view & manage their membership card, transaction history, loaded value, rewards, discounts, transfers, benefits, & more.

- Receive team push notifications based on breaking news, start of game, end of quarter, or final score.

- Shop Hawks Shop, the official retail store of the Atlanta Hawks.

- Connect with us on social media.

- Sign up for team emails, promotions, and contests.
